If none, state "None" Name Date submitted Rodolfo Chinchilla 02-94 10. That I have submitted visa petition(s) to the Immigration and Naturalization Service on behalf of the following person(s). For example, if you intend to furnish room and board, state for how long and, if money, state the amount in United States dollars and state whether it is to be given in a lump sum, weekly, or monthly, or for how long.)
